gomodel:SYNGO_1249  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099060 replaced by GO:0099634" , "Rationale: Here we report on the subcellular localiza- tion of these receptors in the SCN, as revealed by an exten- sively characterized antibody to the\n\n12/9/2017 Pim\n- Literal: \" Panel (e) shows presynaptic (arrow) and postsynaptic (arrowheads) location of immunogold particles, while a clear presynaptic expression (arrows) of GABAA receptor is in panel (f)\"\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Fourteen adult rats of the Sprague-Dawley strain were used for light and electron microscopic immunocytochemical analysis of GABAA receptors in the SCN." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9425-2935" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
